Available Tools: get_ticket_status | list_open_tickets | add_reply | close_ticket | reopen_ticket
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "ticket_id": "string", "customer_id": "string", "reply": "string" }
Response Schema: { "ticket_id": "string", "status": "open|in_progress|resolved|closed", "replies": [{ "author": "string", "message": "string", "timestamp": "string" }] }
---
Question: Could you verify the current status of ticket T-1102 for customer C-773 and check if the billing team has responded?
Call: { "func_call": "get_ticket_status", "ticket_id": "T-1102", "customer_id": "C-773", "reply": "" }
Response: { "ticket_id": "T-1102", "status": "in_progress", "replies": [{ "author": "Support Agent Elena", "message": "Your invoice dispute has been forwarded to the billing department for review.", "timestamp": "2023-10-25T08:15:00Z" }] }

Question: Please add a comment to ticket T-3398 for customer C-221 informing them that their feature request has been added to the roadmap.
Call: { "func_call": "add_reply", "ticket_id": "T-3398", "customer_id": "C-221", "reply": "We have logged your feature request and it is now part of our product roadmap for Q1 next year." }
Response: { "ticket_id": "T-3398", "status": "open", "replies": [{ "author": "Customer C-221", "message": "Can you add dark mode to the mobile app?", "timestamp": "2023-10-25T09:00:00Z" }, { "author": "Support Agent Ben", "message": "We have logged your feature request and it is now part of our product roadmap for Q1 next year.", "timestamp": "2023-10-25T09:20:00Z" }] }

